title: Cardi B Battles Surf Shop Model Over Tattoo
description:
Cardi B has always been one for the shock and awe, but this time it may have been too much! Tune in as we talk about how her use of a tattoo on a mixtape cover may lead to her owing millions to a surf-shop worker.
